BT 1 0 0 1 0 230 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (The advent of large language models \(LLMs\) has ushered in a new paradigm of search engines) Tj T* (that use generative models to gather and summarize information to answer user queries. This) Tj T* -0.028701 Tw (emerging technology, which we formalize under the unified framework of generative engines \(GEs\),) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.084037 Tw (can generate accurate and personalized responses, rapidly replacing traditional search engines like) Tj T* 0 Tw (Google and Bing. Generative Engines typically satisfy queries by synthesizing information from) Tj T* (multiple sources and summarizing them using LLMs. While this shift significantly improves user) Tj T* (utility and generative search engine traffic, it poses a huge challenge for the third stakeholder \226) Tj T* (website and content creators. Given the black-box and fast-moving nature of generative engines,) Tj T* (content creators have little to no control over when and how their content is displayed. With) Tj T* (generative engines here to stay, we must ensure the creator economy is not disadvantaged. To) Tj T* (address this, we introduce Generative Engine Optimization \(GEO\), the first novel paradigm to aid) Tj T* (content creators in improving their content visibility in generative engine responses through a) Tj T* (flexible black-box optimization framework for optimizing and defining visibility metrics. We facilitate) Tj T* (systematic evaluation by introducing GEO-bench, a large-scale benchmark of diverse user queries) Tj T* (across multiple domains, along with relevant web sources to answer these queries. Through) Tj T* (rigorous evaluation, we demonstrate that GEO can boost visibility by up to $4 0 \\%$ in generative) Tj T* (engine responses. Moreover, we show the efficacy of these strategies varies across domains,) Tj T* (underscoring the need for domain-specific optimization methods. Our work opens a new frontier in) Tj T* (information discovery systems, with profound implications for both developers of generative) Tj T* (engines and content creators.1) Tj T* ET
