BT 1 0 0 1 0 110 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (The usefulness of generative engines for developers and users is evident \226 users access) Tj T* (information faster and more accurately, while developers craft precise and personalized responses,) Tj T* (improving user satisfaction and revenue. However, generative engines disadvantage the third) Tj T* (stakeholder \226 website and content creators. Generative Engines, in contrast to traditional search) Tj T* (engines, remove the need to navigate to websites by directly providing a precise and) Tj T* (comprehensive response, potentially reducing organic traffic to websites and impacting their) Tj T* (visibility [16]. With millions of small businesses and individuals relying on online traffic and visibility) Tj T* (for their livelihood, generative engines will significantly disrupt the creator economy. Further, the) Tj T* (black-box and proprietary nature of generative engines makes it difficult for content creators to) Tj T* (control and understand how their content is ingested and portrayed.) Tj T* ET
