BT 1 0 0 1 0 62 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (In this work, we propose the first general creator-centric framework to optimize content for) Tj T* (generative engines, which we dub Generative Engine Optimization \(GEO\), to empower content) Tj T* (creators to navigate this new search paradigm. GEO is a flexible black-box optimization framework) Tj T* (for optimizing web content visibility for proprietary and closed-source generative engines \(Figure 1\).) Tj T* (GEO ingests a source website and outputs an optimized version by tailoring and calibrating the) Tj T* (presentation, text style, and content to increase visibility in generative engines.) Tj T* ET
