BT 1 0 0 1 0 146 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (While individual GEO strategies show significant improvements across various domains, in) Tj T* (practice, website owners are expected to employ multiple strategies in conjunction. To study the) Tj T* (performance improvements achieved by combining GEO strategies, we consider all pairs of) Tj T* (combinations of the top 4 performing GEO methods, namely Cite Sources, Fluency Optimization,) Tj T* (Statistics Addition, and Quotation Addition. Figure 4 displays the heatmap of relative improvement) Tj T* (in the Position-Adjusted Word Count visibility metric achieved by combining different GEO) Tj T* (strategies. The analysis demonstrates that the combination of Generative Engine Optimization) Tj T* (methods can enhance performance, with the best combination \(Fluency Optimization and Statistics) Tj T* (Addition\) outperforming any single GEO strategy by more than $5 . 5 \\% ^ { 4 }$ . Furthermore, Cite) Tj T* (Sources significantly boosts performance when used in conjunction with other methods \(Average:) Tj T* ($3 1 . 4 \\%$ \), despite it being relatively less effective when used alone $8 \\%$ lower than) Tj T* (Quotation Addition\). The findings underscore the importance of studying GEO methods in) Tj T* (combination, as they are likely to be used by content creators in the real world.) Tj T* ET
