BT 1 0 0 1 0 146 Tm /F1 10 Tf 12 TL (While we rigorously test our proposed methods on two generative engines, including a publicly) Tj T* (available one, methods may need to adapt over time as GEs evolve, mirroring the evolution of) Tj T* (SEO. Additionally, despite our efforts to ensure the queries in our GEObench closely resemble) Tj T* (real-world queries, the nature of queries can change over time, necessitating continuous updates.) Tj T* (Further, owing to the black-box nature of search engine algorithms, we didn\222t evaluate how GEO) Tj T* (methods affect search rankings. However, we note that changes made by GEO methods are) Tj T* (targeted changes in textual content, bearing some resemblance with SEO methods, while not) Tj T* (affecting other metadata such as domain name, backlinks, etc, and thus, they are less likely to) Tj T* (affect search engine rankings. Further, as larger context lengths in language models become) Tj T* (economical, it is expected that future generative models will be able to ingest more sources, thus) Tj T* (reducing the impact of search rankings. Lastly, while every query in our proposed GEO-bench is) Tj T* (tagged and manually inspected, there may be discrepancies due to subjective interpretations or) Tj T* (errors in labeling.) Tj T* ET
